":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"团队容易只看“功能交付速度”，忽略“未来一年维护投入”。"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"质量文化淡化：\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"如果管理层只追求“AI 提效指标”，工程师自然会在质量标准上“向下对齐”。"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"知识沉淀路径变化：\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"原本通过手写和重构沉淀的“隐性知识”，被部分转移到“提示语”和“过往生成代码”中。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"如果缺乏规范的共享指令与知识库建设，这些知识很难被团队系统地复用。"}]}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"hr","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"六落地建议在生产中负责任地用-ai"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"六、落地建议：在生产中“负责任地用 AI”"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"_61-强化并嵌入既有实践tdd-与静态分析"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"6.1 强化并嵌入既有实践：TDD 与静态分析"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"原文明确提出："},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"在生产环境中有效使用 AI，需要重新强化代码质量实践，尤其是 TDD 和静态分析，并把它们嵌入到开发流中。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"一个可操作的落地思路是："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"对 TDD 的强化：\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"明确要求“AI 生成代码前先定义测试”，或者让 AI 先生成测试 skeleton，再填实现。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"在 review checklist 中加入“测试先行/测试充分性”项，而不仅是“代码可读性”。"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"对静态分析的升级：\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"针对 AI 生成特点增加规则，例如：\n- 重复逻辑检测；\n- 可疑大函数/大类的警报；\n- magic number / 无注释复杂逻辑的提示。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"将静态分析结果纳入 CI 阶段的“硬门槛”，而不是可选提示。"}]}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"_62-利用共享指令把规范写进工作流"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"6.2 利用“共享指令”把规范写进工作流"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"原文提到的一个关键建议是："},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"通过精心策划的“共享指令集”（curated shared instructions）直接嵌入团队的编码工作流"}]},{"type":"text","value":"。这在实践中可以演化为："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"团队级系统提示（system / team prompt）：\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"固定质量原则：如“禁止复制粘贴大段代码”、“需要解释复杂逻辑意图”等。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"约束生成范围：例如“严禁改动超出当前模块边界的代码”。"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"场景化模板：\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"不同任务类型（bug 修复 / 新功能 / 重构 / 跨模块变更）对应不同的提示模板和 review checklist。"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"持续演化机制：\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"将线上事故、review 发现的问题沉淀为新指令，不断迭代团队共享 prompt。"}]}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"这样做的目标是："},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"把“经验性规范”变成“系统性约束”，并让 AI 自身也遵守这些约束"}]},{"type":"text","value":"。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"_63-控制变更粒度与审查策略"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"6.3 控制变更粒度与审查策略"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"对于 coding agents 特别需要注意："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"限制单次变更范围：\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"在提示中明确“一个任务只改一个有界上下文/子系统”，减少超大 diff。"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"强化自动化保护网：\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"为 agent 生成的改动配置更严格的测试门槛和预发布验证流程。"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"采用分阶段 rollout：\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"对高风险变更采用灰度发布、分流验证，并要求 agent 输出“变更点清单”和“潜在影响区域”。"}]}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"_64-识别不适用场景与风险边界"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"6.4 识别不适用场景与风险边界"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"在以下场景中，应更加谨慎使用 AI 直接生成或大规模修改代码："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"高安全/高合规要求系统（金融、隐私敏感业务等）；"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"对领域建模要求极高、规则复杂且多变的核心域；"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"现有代码库已高度耦合，缺乏测试与观测基础，无法有效回归与监控。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"对于这些场景，更合理的策略通常是："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"优先用 AI 做辅助分析、重构建议、测试生成，而非直接放权给 agent 做大规模改动；"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"先补齐测试和监控能力，再逐步扩大 AI 参与范围。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"综合来看，原文的核心立场并不是“反对 AI 编程”，而是明确提醒："},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"AI 提速的是“编码”这一局部环节，但代价是在系统层面增加了质量管理的复杂度和认知风险"}]},{"type":"text","value":"。要在生产中有效使用这类工具，技术负责人需要把 TDD、静态分析、review 规范等实践重新“嵌入工作流”，并通过共享指令和流程设计，把团队的质量文化编码进 AI 使用方式，而不是寄希望于“更聪明的模型自动抵消这些风险”。"}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"brief","depth":2,"text":"Brief"},{"id":"details","depth":2,"text":"Details","children":[{"id":"一背景与现状从提效工具到系统性质量压力","depth":3,"text":"一、背景与现状：从“提效工具”到“系统性质量压力”"},{"id":"二问题与风险惰性依赖的技术与组织后果","depth":3,"text":"二、问题与风险：惰性依赖的技术与组织后果"},{"id":"三模式与原理从快写到系统配平","depth":3,"text":"三、模式与原理：从“快写”到“系统配平”"},{"id":"四对比与演进ai-工具前后的工程形态","depth":3,"text":"四、对比与演进：AI 工具前后的工程形态"},{"id":"五系统影响对架构工程效率与协作的牵引","depth":3,"text":"五、系统影响：对架构、工程效率与协作的牵引"},{"id":"六落地建议在生产中负责任地用-ai","depth":3,"text":"六、落地建议：在生产中“负责任地用 AI”"}]}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:6.maps:_ai:vibe:complacency.md","_source":"content","_file":"6.maps/_ai/vibe/complacency.md","_stem":"6.maps/_ai/vibe/complacency","_extension":"md"}